{"tid":241832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旗下公司遭中國公司收購　漫威之父Stan Lee：正創作兩名中國超級英雄","createTime":"2017-05-13T12:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T06:24:34.000Z","uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6536847f4be8c51aeccde665229bf41a86162db","tid":241832,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:42:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>旗下公司遭中國公司收購　漫威之父Stan Lee：正創作兩名中國超級英雄</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/C8wZDRjVYAAouRO_KfOiK_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FC8wZDRjVYAAouRO_KfOiK_1200x0.jpg&h=aa9ec8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStan Lee (相：Stan Lee Twitter專頁）<br />\n<br />\n蜘蛛俠、雷神、Iron Man的原作者Stan Lee，旗下的娛樂公司早前被香港上市的大陸文化產業集團承興國際收購，新華社近日訪問94歲的Stan Lee，他表示正著手塑造中國的超級英雄形象&mdash;一名男英雄和一名女英雄。<br />\n<br />\n新華網報道，承興國際收購的是Stan Lee旗下的POW！娛樂，是專門開發與授權超級英雄創意的公司，其版權庫中擁有270個正在開發的項目和超過1000個角色。收購後，Stan Lee仍擔任公司創意總監一職。<br />\n<br />\nStan Lee提到，中國夥伴提供了資金和建議。「現在我們有能力製作更多的電影，將有更多的資金來完善我們的項目。」<br />\n<br />\n他又透露，已開始製作中國的超級英雄，「我們將更多地關注中國市場和亞洲市場，增加有關中國的故事和創意，事實上我們已經開始塑造中國的超級英雄形象&mdash;一名男英雄和一名女英雄。」他表示，以後會在創作中加入更多中國元素。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，蜘蛛俠雖然不是中國面孔，但在中國和全世界都大受歡迎，可見一個超級英雄形象是否成功，在於人物個性的塑造。<br />\n<br />\nStan Lee在漫威公司（Marvel）工作逾60年，創造了多個著名超級英雄角色，他至今仍兼任漫威影業的榮譽主席和漫威漫畫編輯委員會成員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1684618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thepaper.cn%2FnewsDetail_forward_1684618&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=97d5a6ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1684618</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E9%81%AD%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC-%E6%BC%AB%E5%A8%81%E4%B9%8B%E7%88%B6stan-lee-%E6%AD%A3%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%A9%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%2597%2597%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC-%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E5%25A8%2581%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%2588%25B6stan-lee-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%2589%25B5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%25B4%259A%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%259B%2584%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=9414101e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%2597%2597%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC-%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E5%25A8%2581%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%2588%25B6stan-lee-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%2589%25B5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B6%2585%25E7%25B4%259A%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%259B%2584%2F&h=6a6dc80f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E9%81%AD%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC-%E6%BC%AB%E5%A8%81%E4%B9%8B%E7%88%B6stan-lee-%E6%AD%A3%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%A9%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84/</a>"},{"pid":"b2cfdde588c7b4b7ba59ef8258c6057476a0bd6e","tid":241832,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abbe3f747a33de859a14c2a2b27e319dd47d97c","tid":241832,"uid":56878,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:46:24.000Z","msg":"Marvel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係dc好"},{"pid":"98008577cedd85952e1d